    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-02-21) predates the model revision of 2025-03-17 by 24 days; the assessment team reviewed the revision change log and determined that modifications to near-wall turbulence closure constants were not material to the hemolysis scalar transport correlation validated against that dataset. On this basis the prior validation evidence is accepted without re-execution. Overall credibility assessment: Accepted for CPB use submission.",
